Malo agha ghakaŵa ghakutowa chomene pa nyengo ya holide.
Mwaciyelezgero, mungaluta ku nyumba zacifumu za ku Loire Valley, ku Rhine Valley, panji ku malo ghakuzirwa gha ku Danube River.
Ghakulongoraso nthowa izo ŵanthu ŵakwenda pakukwera mapiri na pa njinga.
Khisimasi ntchimoza mwa vikondwelero vyakuzirwa chomene vya Chikhristu ndipo yikukondwelera kubabika kwa Yesu.
Vinthu vinandi ivyo vikuchitika pa Khisimasi, ŵanthu ŵambura kusopa awo ŵakukhala mu vyaru ivyo vikuti ni Vyachikhristu na awo Mbakhristu yayi ŵali kutolerako.
Ŵanthu ŵakutemwa kukhala pawaro usiku wa pa Isitara kuti ŵawone dazi likufuma.
Ŵanthu awo ŵakasopanga ŵachiuta ŵatesi ŵakakondweleranga yayi Khisimasi.
Matchalitchi agho ghakusopa mwakuyana na kaluso ka ŵanthu, kanandi ghakuŵa na Paska pa Sabata mise mu Sabata Yikuru, ndipo kanandi mipingo yikuwungana usiku pakati kukondwelera kuwuka kwa Khristu.
Vinyama vyose ivyo vikambanga kukhala pa virwa ivi, vikafikanga pa virwa ivi mwa kuskamba, kuduka, panji kwiza pa maji.
Vinyama ivi vikatondeka kwenda mtunda utali, ntheura somba zikuruzikuru ndizo zikurya vyakurya vinandi mu virwa ivi.
Kufuma waka apo ŵanthu ŵakambira kukhala mu virwa vya Galapagos, ŵakiza na vinyama vinandi, nga ni mbuzi, mahachi, ng'ombe, mbeŵa, mphaka, na ntcheŵe.
Usange mungaluta ku malo ghakucemeka Arctic panji Antarctic mu nyengo ya ciwuvi, mungakumana na usiku uwo zuŵa likuleka kufuma.
Iyi ni nyengo yiwemi chomene yakuwonera mabingu gha kumpoto chifukwa nyengo iyi mtambo ukuŵa mu mdima.
Pakuti malo agha ghali na ŵanthu ŵachoko, ndipo ungweru waŵalirapo yayi, mungadokera kuwona nyenyezi.
Ŵanthu ŵa ku Japan ŵakutemwa kugwira ntchito za malipiro ghanandi kuluska ŵanthu ŵa ku vyaru vya ŵazungu.
Ŵanthu awo ŵakugwira lumoza nchito ŵakucemana mazina panji kucemana na udindo wawo.
Kuŵa ŵakukolerana pa nchito nkhwakuzirwa comene, ndipo cinthu cakuzirwa comene nkhucitira vinthu pamoza m'malo mwa kucita vinthu mwekha.
Kanandi ŵantchito ŵakwenera kukolerana na ŵabwana ŵawo pa chilichose icho ŵakuchita, ndipo ŵakukhazga waka kuti ŵapulikirenge ulongozgi wawo.
